LOS ANGELES , May 19 , 2014 ( BUSINESS WIRE ) -- AECOM Technology Corporation ACM , +1.21 % a leading provider of professional technical and management support services for public and private clients in more than 150 countries around the world , invites investors and other interested parties to listen to a live webcast of its presentation by senior management on May 21 , beginning at 6:30 p.m. PDT .

AECOM provides a blend of global reach , local knowledge , innovation and technical excellence in delivering solutions that create , enhance and sustain the world 's built , natural , and social environments .
A Fortune 500 company ,  AECOM serves clients in more than 150 countries and had revenue of  $ 8.0 billion during the 12 months ended March 31 , 2014 .
